item.description:
Facebook Garage Ireland - Live Music Mashup App Rich Media Video Presentation - Gig Monkey (Mobile Phone, Last FM, Bebo, Amazon, iLike, Facebook Connect)
Available to view on FACEBOOK http://www.facebook.com/video/video.php?v=1178217701817 and
VIMEO http://www.vimeo.com/5675891
This is a rich media visual presentation of a Facebook Live Music Mobile Phone Mash-up Application called Gig Monkey, using Amazon AWS, Last FM API, iLike and Facebook Connect. Presented by Sean O'Sullivan, Rococosoft.com, Sponsored by Facebook Garage Ireland/Facebook EMEA and Enterprise-Ireland.com, Hosted by Web2Ireland.org and Produced and Directed by PathPacific.com

item.title: By: Kieran Daly
item.dc:creator: Kieran Daly
item.description:
Great thanks for sharing the PPTs. It great that people share these out as there is so much social media action now going on in Ireland that it is hard to make all of them especially we people down in Cork.
Must arrange a Cork event at some stage as the buzz around Social Media 2.0/3.0 and beyond is growing so fast.
